originalText.text: Eventually, this is business when time, presentation, research, professional knowledge and personal skills translate into capital. Virginia happens to have all of those. She helped us to sell our townhouse. Though not my first choice (family and national descent come first...), I was happy to switch to work with Virginia simply on my gut feeling. She is a soft cyclone. Be assured she is working when you sleep.
